{"id":"entities/lincoln-jazz-center","title":"Lincoln Jazz Center (Shanghai)","type":"entities","html":"<h1>Lincoln Jazz Center (Shanghai)</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. First mentioned in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-09-05-shanghai-sidequests\">2024 09 05 shanghai sidequests</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Shanghai venue affiliated with Wynton Marsalis's Jazz at Lincoln Center. Aligns with Yahir's recurring <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ahmad-jamal\">jazz interest</a> (see also <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/bill-evans\">bill evans</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/john-coltrane\">john coltrane</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/miles-davis\">miles davis</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/louis-armstrong\">louis armstrong</a>).</p>\n<h2>Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/shanghai\">shanghai</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">china chapter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/ahmad-jamal\">ahmad jamal</a></li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/ahmad-jamal","label":"Ahmad Jamal"},{"id":"entities/bill-evans","label":"Bill Evans"},{"id":"concepts/china-chapter","label":"China Chapter"},{"id":"entities/john-coltrane","label":"John Coltrane"},{"id":"entities/louis-armstrong","label":"Louis Armstrong"},{"id":"summaries/2022-05-06-to-do-osig-flip-phone","label":"May 2022 to-do — OSIG workbook, Bob Dylan ticket, flip-phone aspiration"},{"id":"entities/miles-davis","label":"Miles Davis"},{"id":"entities/shanghai","label":"Shanghai"},{"id":"summaries/2024-09-05-shanghai-sidequests","label":"Shanghai Sidequests — bucket list during the China chapter"}]}
